headline: Wall Street Analysts Think Allstate (ALL) Is a Good Investment: Is It?
summary: The average brokerage recommendation (ABR) for Allstate (ALL) is equivalent to a Buy. The overly optimistic recommendations of Wall Street analysts make the effectiveness of this highly sought-after metric questionable. So, is it worth buying the stock?

headline: Corebridge Financial Announces Availability of Life Insurance Products Through Allstate Financial Services
summary: HOUSTON, September 30, 2025--Corebridge Financial today announced countrywide availability of its life insurance products through Allstate Financial Services, LLC, representing a strategic addition to the distribution partner network for the Corebridge Life Insurance business. Corebridge will bring its broad portfolio of competitive life insurance products to licensed Allstate sales professionals and customers across the United States.
